com.mashery.trafficmanager.model.core

Interface Key

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    APIKey, PackageKey

    public interface Key
    API Key that identifies the Application making the request. A Key may have an owner and may belong to a Developer Class
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Application getApplication()
      Returns this Key's application or null if none
      ExtendedAttributes getExtendedAttributes()
      Returns this Key's extended attributes.
      String getExternalID()
      Returns this Key's external identifier.
      User getOwner()
      Returns this Key's owner or null if none.
      RateConstraint getRateConstraint()
      Returns this Key's rate constraint, or null if none is configured on this Key, or if this Key belongs to a Developer Class and the User Class does not allow rate constraint overriding, or the Endpoint itself does not allow rate constraint overriding by Keys.
      ThrottleConstraint getThrottleConstraint()
      Returns this Key's throttle constraint, or null if none is configured on this Key, or if this Key belongs to a Developer Class and the Developer Class does not allow throttle constraint overriding, or the Endpoint itself does not allow throttle constraint overriding by Keys.
